      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my dad just got in from his flight from tokyo and he's saying his left arm feels really heavy and tingly, almost like it's asleep. he also mentioned his speech sounds a bit thick/slurred like he's tired. he thinks he's just super exhausted from the long trip and needs to sleep it off. is that normal after a flight like that?",
